outside of the disk as shown, and starts at unstretched length [`x_0=[$x0]cm`] when the rod is horizontal. 

If the rod is released from rest at the horizontal position shown, What is the angular velocity after it has rotated [`90^\circ`]?

You can neglect the thickness of the rod and friction forces.

[`{\omega}=`][___]{"$omega"} [`rad/s`]


 _Round your answers to three decimal places_.


